description: Describes the current status of a mailbox export job.

nested_items.name: EntityId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the user or resource associated with the mailbox.

nested_items.name: RoleArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the AWS Identity and Access Management (IAM) role that grants write permission to the Amazon Simple Storage Service (Amazon S3) bucket.

nested_items.name: KmsKeyArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the symmetric AWS Key Management Service (AWS KMS) key that encrypts the exported mailbox content.

nested_items.name: S3BucketName
nested_items.description: The name of the S3 bucket.

nested_items.name: S3Path
nested_items.description: The path to the S3 bucket and file that the mailbox export job is exporting to.

nested_items.name: EstimatedProgress
nested_items.description: The estimated progress of the mailbox export job, in percentage points.

nested_items.name: State
nested_items.description: The state of the mailbox export job.

nested_items.name: ErrorInfo
nested_items.description: Error information for failed mailbox export jobs.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The mailbox export job start timestamp.

nested_items.name: EndTime
nested_items.description: The mailbox export job end timestamp.
